RoutingInfo.AdditionalInformation: Number portability was introduced on November 29 2011. This means that Cable & Wireless Panama customers can have a MSISDN, which is takenfrom any Panama mobile network NDC. In Panama we have other 3 mobile companies: Claro, Telefonica and Digicel.
